    <category>BBQ</category>
    <category>BBQ</category>
  </category>
  <preparation><![CDATA[Mix together salt, mustard fennel, coriander, cinnamon and red pepper; crushing in the fennel seeds in a mortar & pestle or against the side of the bowl with a strong metal spoon. 

Rinse and pat dry chicken breasts and evenly coat all sides with spice mixture.

Grill chicken and prepare sauce:  mix olive oil, cilantro, lemon juice, garlic and a dash of salt in a small bowl.  Drizzle oil mixture over chicken just prior to serving.

Olive oil mix may be made ahead of time and chilled -- the difference in temperatures between the oil and the chicken is rather pleasant.]]></preparation>
</recipe>
